      "created": 1781838314,
      "updated": 1781838314
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34b1e70000000000e411ac",
      "text": " [ヘロドトス]の[政体循環史観]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1781838314,
      "updated": 1781838345
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34b20d0000000000e411ae",
      "text": "  https://www.y-history.net/appendix/wh0103-174_2.html",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1781838351,
      "updated": 1781838352
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34b1e80000000000e411ad",
      "text": " [ソシオニクス]研究者（[グレンコ]）の[ソシオン]の時計 ",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1781838314,
      "updated": 1781838438
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34b2640000000000e411b0",
      "text": "  https://wikisocion.github.io/content/socion_clock.html",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1781838438,
      "updated": 1781838456
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34b2760000000000e411b1",
      "text": "  こちらは似非科学なので注意が必要[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1781838457,
      "updated": 1781838464
    },
